MenuConfigurationControls.SensitivityScalingMode_ProjectionRatio_T: Scale by ratio between active FOV projected onto screen and configured FOV projected onto screen.

MenuConfigurationGraphics.Ambient_Occlusion_Tooltip: Soft shading near corners and contacts.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Bloom_Tooltip: Blur glowing halo around bright lights.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Chromatic_Aberration_Tooltip: Lens imperfection maybe useful for screenshots.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Film_Grain_Tooltip: Add subtle visual noise to reduce color banding.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Blend_Tooltip: Blend terrain textures according to per-material heightmaps rather than a basic linear blend.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Grass_Displacement_Tooltip: Basic vertex displacement around player feet.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Wind_Tooltip: Vertex animation for objects affected by wind.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Foliage_Focus_Tooltip: While zoomed-in stream foliage around the focal point.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Debris_Tooltip: Simulate physics for debris when an object is destroyed.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Blast_Toggle_Tooltip: Spawn 3D decals at explosions. Performance is affected by number of overlapping pixels on screen.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Puddle_Tooltip: Puddle and ripple effects for raindrops.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Triplanar_Tooltip: Aligns boulder textures with the terrain by sampling three textures per pixel rather than one.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Skybox_Reflection_Tooltip: Render dynamic skybox into a cubemap for ambient lighting and reflections.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Item_Icon_Anti_Aliasing_Tooltip: Prevents jagged pixel edges on inventory item icons.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Anisotropic_Filtering_Button_Tooltip: Reduce texture blur at oblique angles
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Water_Button_Tooltip: Water transparency, foam, waves and reflections
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Render_Mode_Button_Tooltip: Forward might run better on older graphics cards, Deferred allows decals and screen space reflections
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Landmark_Button_Tooltip: Extremely low detail models for extended view distance
MenuConfigurationGraphics.AA_Hint: Deferred rendering and MSAA are incompatible
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Perf_Foliage_Instancing_Not_Supported: Your GPU does not support foliage instancing. This will significantly affect performance.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Perf_Water_Reflections: Ultra enables planar reflections. These require drawing the scene again upside-down, halving performance.
MenuConfigurationGraphics.Perf_Dual_Render_Scope: Dual-render scopes require drawing the scene again zoomed-in, halving performance.

MenuConfigurationOptions.Filter_Toggle_Tooltip: Note: hate speech is censored regardless of whether profanity filter is enabled.
MenuConfigurationOptions.VoiceAlwaysRecording_Tooltip: Avoid hitches related to starting and stopping recording by muting rather than stopping.
MenuConfigurationOptions.ShowOutboundVoiceChatOffHint_Tooltip: Shows a muted icon in HUD when outbound voice chat is off.
MenuConfigurationOptions.Nametag_Fade_Out_Tooltip: Makes group member name labels more transparent near the center of your crosshair.
MenuConfigurationOptions.ScreenshotSizeMultiplier_Tooltip: Higher values take significantly longer to render.
MenuConfigurationOptions.ScreenshotSupersampling_Tooltip: Render screenshots with 2x supersampling to reduce aliasing.
MenuConfigurationOptions.ScreenshotsWhileLoading_Tooltip: Enable your own screenshots on the startup loading screen.
MenuConfigurationOptions.UseStaticCrosshair_Tooltip: Use custom crosshair size rather than size calculated from spread.
MenuConfigurationOptions.Metric_Tooltip: Affects display of distance and speed.
MenuConfigurationOptions.Talk_Tooltip: Instant disables dialogue pauses and the per-letter animation.
MenuConfigurationOptions.UI_Tooltip: Light is more useful when combined with the UI color options from the Gold Upgrade.
MenuConfigurationOptions.Hitmarker_Tooltip: Static places hitmarkers in the center of the screen, whereas Dynamic tracks the 3D hit.
MenuConfigurationOptions.DontShowOnlineSafetyMenuAgain_Label: Don't show Online Safety menu again
MenuConfigurationOptions.DontShowOnlineSafetyMenuAgain_Tooltip: If checked, the Online Safety menu won't be shown the next time you open multiplayer. (Unless you haven't opened it before.)

MenuTips.Hotkey: You can hotkey an item in your hands slot by right-clicking it and then pressing a number key [3-9].

MenuTips.Drop: You can quickly drop an item by holding [{0}] while left-clicking it.
MenuTips.Sirens: You can turn the sirens in a police vehicle on/off by pressing [{0}] as the driver.
MenuTips.Transform: You can copy transforms in the editor by pressing Ctrl+B and paste them by pressing Ctrl+N.
MenuTips.Quality: Your ranger weapons and attachments are more durable than their military counterparts.
MenuTips.Umbrella: You can use umbrellas to lower your falling speed and prevent fall damage.
MenuTips.Heal: You can heal other players by right-clicking on them while holding a medical item.
MenuTips.Rotate: You can rotate objects while building by holding right-click while dragging the mouse.
MenuTips.Base: Your crafting materials impacts stats and from best to worst are: <color=rare>Brick</color> -> <color=epic>Metal</color> -> <color=rare>Pine</color> -> <color=uncommon>Maple</color> -> <color=common>Birch</color>
MenuTips.Dequip: You can quickly dequip an item by pressing [{0}].
MenuTips.Nightvision: You can turn nightvision and headlamps on/off by pressing [{0}].
MenuTips.Transfer: You can quickly transfer an item in/out of storage by holding [{0}] while right-clicking it.
MenuTips.Surface: You can quickly surface while swimming by holding [{0}].
MenuTips.Arrest: You can eventually wiggle your way out of restraints by repeatedly tapping [{0}] and [{1}].
MenuTips.Safezone: You can protect an area from zombie spawns by placing a <color=legendary>Safezone Radiator</color>, but it also blocks item spawns.
MenuTips.Claim: You can prevent players from building in an area by placing a <color=legendary>Claim Flag</color>.
MenuTips.Group: You can join a group with your friends to disable friendlyfire, share buildables, see eachother on the map and win arena as a team.
MenuTips.Map: You can view a map of the area if you have a <color=uncommon>Chart</color> or <color=epic>GPS</color> by pressing [{0}].
MenuTips.Beacon: You can summon a wave of zombies for great loot drops by placing a <color=legendary>Horde Beacon</color>.
MenuTips.Horn: You can use the horn of a vehicle by pressing [{0}] as the driver.
MenuTips.Lights: You can turn the headlights in a vehicle on/off by pressing [{0}] as the driver.
MenuTips.Snap: You can snap an object's position and rotation by holding [{0}].
MenuTips.Upgrade: You can quickly craft all of an item or fully upgrade a skill by holding [{0}] while clicking it.
MenuTips.Grab: You can quickly grab an item from a rifle rack by holding [{0}] while interacting with it.
MenuTips.Skycrane: You can activate the <color=epic>Skycrane</color>'s electromagnet by pressing [{0}] while hovering over a vehicle.
MenuTips.Seat: You can swap seats in a vehicle by pressing the function keys [F1-F12].
MenuTips.Rarity: Your loot's rarity from best to worst is: <color=mythical>Mythical</color> -> <color=legendary>Legendary</color> -> <color=epic>Epic</color> -> <color=rare>Rare</color> -> <color=uncommon>Uncommon</color> -> <color=common>Common</color>
MenuTips.Orientation: You can rotate items in your inventory by pressing [{0}].
MenuTips.Red: Your critical hitmarker color setting also affects the color of glowing sights.
MenuTips.Steady: You can steady your scope by holding [{0}] while aiming. Remember to account for bullet drop and travel time!
MenuTips.Streamer: You can customize the names used in streamer mode by modifying StreamerNames.json, maybe with viewer/subscriber names!
MenuTips.SkipActionCraftingMenu: You can skip the crafting menu when performing an action in an item's context menu by holding [{0}] while clicking it.

PlayerLife.Tutorial_Move: Hey there! Are you alive? Move [{0}, {1}, {2}, {3}] around a bit, get your blood flowing!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Look: Okay phew! Can you View [Drag Mouse] my camera in the corner?
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Jump: Looking good! Jump [{0}] over this ledge. This can save your life when you're being chased!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Perspective: Looking so good that you might want a peek for yourself! Get a different Perspective [{0}] on life.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Run: Wait, nevermind jumping, sometimes it's best to just Run [{0}] away from danger!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Inventory: Here's some nice clothes for you! Interact [{0}] to get a bit of space for storing your gear.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Survival: The basic necessities of life! You can equip or drop them from your Inventory [{0}] with [{1}] after picking them up.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Gun: Finally a chance for some action! Aim [{0}] and Shoot [{1}] your gun at those zombies.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Ladder: Nice shooting! Next time maybe climb down the ladder by walking backwards onto it rather than jumping in...
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Craft: View your Attachments [{0}] and select the magazine to remove it, then Craft [{1}] it with these bullets in the ammo category to restock it.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Skills: Use some of those experience points you got from the zombies to level up your Skills [{0}] in each category!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Swim: Navigate through that cave and Surface [{0}] on the other side.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Medical: Use [{0}] these medical supplies if you're feeling wounded! Note: I have no liability for any injuries sustained.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Vehicle: Siphon [{0}] the fuel tank into the gas can, then Fuel [{1}] this vehicle to Drive [{2}] to the other end.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Crouch: Sneaking with Crouch [{0}] is vital to avoid zombie detection, and allows you through small spaces.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Prone: At the cost of speed you can also go Prone [{0}] which is far sneakier than crouching!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Educated: You've completed your basic training! Pause [{0}] to leave, or stay and see a few advanced activities.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Harvest: Scavenge [{0}] for berries, chop down trees and hunt animals to survive in the wilderness!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Fish: Fishing requires patience and deep water. Cast [{0}] your line and Reel [{0}] it in when you see the bob go under.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Build: Building a base is key to your survival, and spans from tiny traps to giant walls. You can even build vehicles!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Lights: Use your Headlights [{0}] to see further in the dark.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Sirens: Show the bandits you mean business with your Sirens [{0}]!
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Farm: Farming provides a sustainable source of food.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Power: Generators can power electrical objects such as anti-zombie radiators and traffic lights.
PlayerLife.Tutorial_Fire: Fires keep you warm in freezing environments and give you an easy place to Cook [{0}] food.
